{"tid":2119489,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醫護凍薪，清算罷工，唔封關等醫療崩潰，原來係為咗。。","createTime":"2020-07-22T06:36:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T11:57:04.000Z","uid":53000,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4e51b269aa6e581a41872b8ae81d00c9431cb058","tid":2119489,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:36:11.000Z","msg":"香港商報：林鄭向中央求助　上海等地醫務人員待命來港支援<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦控制的《香港商報》周二 (21/7) 報道，指有消息稱特首林鄭月娥已向中央求助，如香港武漢肺炎 (COVID-19) 疫情持續惡化，本地醫務系統不堪重負，希望中央協調內地醫務緊急馳援，而上海等地醫務人員已接獲指令待命馳援香港。<br />\n<br />\n現時全港確診感染人數已突破 2,000 人，且有 14 人病死。<br />\n<br />\n該報道以周二衞生署公佈，將兩個病人的病毒檢測結果錯誤調轉，陰性病人被當陽性，曾與一名確診病人在負壓病房共處七小時作例子，指「香港醫療系統所面臨的問題很嚴峻」，又質疑類似烏龍事件可能在疫情惡化下更常出現，稱香港越來越多聲音認為「依靠香港自身力量很難戰勝這一波的疫情」，呼籲特區政府緊急向中央求助。"},{"pid":"34201db9b1a00f3f79d5205631e6d9efa50f52ac","tid":2119489,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:36:42.000Z","msg":"三月香港也曾出現 4 人樣本調亂，兩位陽性病人離開檢測中心返回家居，另外兩位陰性人士則以為確診，一直留在檢測中心等待覆檢結果。<br />\n<br />\n商報報道指，早在 7 月 14 日工聯會已約見林鄭，建議特區政府向中央政府尋求協助，加快全民病毒檢測工作，並指當時林鄭對建議反應正面，傾向尋求中央協助派專業醫療人員來港。"},{"pid":"4db2684ede0a2e11c7c6579ed68facf8fff3b6d8","tid":2119489,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:37:08.000Z","msg":"報道又認為香港在很多地方需要內地的防疫經驗和資源，並在第三波疫情曝露兩大漏洞，一是檢測資源和人手都嚴重不足，追不上病毒的散播速度，二是檢疫中心、公立醫院資源或很快耗盡，稱要模仿內地建設方艙醫院，認為「這些都離不開內地的支援」。該報道最後更指「中國是世界上擁有最豐富防疫經驗，也被公認為抗疫最成功的國家」。<br />\n<br />\n《香港商報》是香港三大親中報紙之一，現時最大股東為聯合出版集團，該集團由中聯辦擁有。<br />\n<br />\n文／Alan Chiu<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%95%86%E5%A0%B1-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E5%90%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E6%B1%82%E5%8A%A9-%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E7%AD%89%E5%9C%B0%E9%86%AB%E5%8B%99%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E5%BE%85%E5%91%BD%E4%BE%86%E6%B8%AF%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E5%2590%2591%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%258A%25A9-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E7%25AD%2589%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%2586%25AB%25E5%258B%2599%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25BE%2585%25E5%2591%25BD%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258F%25B4%2F&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtB7yOm5tzSGwlZJ%2FCF8Wpw90%3D&h=2ce76c02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E5%2590%2591%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%258A%25A9-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E7%25AD%2589%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%2586%25AB%25E5%258B%2599%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25BE%2585%25E5%2591%25BD%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258F%25B4%2F&h=8b51f4d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%95%86%E5%A0%B1-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E5%90%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E6%B1%82%E5%8A%A9-%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E7%AD%89%E5%9C%B0%E9%86%AB%E5%8B%99%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E5%BE%85%E5%91%BD%E4%BE%86%E6%B8%AF%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4/</a>"},{"pid":"1649a2d2286858a634c6a1cdcb5fcf0c460bebe0","tid":2119489,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:37:29.000Z","msg":"<code>Windows Cortana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n<code>請勿引用此回覆。</code>"},{"pid":"de3ba5e34a169a43c8b168baa00b93ea43be95f9","tid":2119489,"uid":64337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />為咗逼害反對聲音<br />\n港共係冇底線"},{"pid":"32f1a792355347a0bca70ca0db7b33ed7464745c","tid":2119489,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:39:54.000Z","msg":"舊聞binC<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n節錄2011年蘋果新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20110510/QQAQLV2AXEYIM55734TZ24ZHY4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20110510%2FQQAQLV2AXEYIM55734TZ24ZHY4%2F&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtB7yOm5tzSGwlZJ%2FCF8Wpw90%3D&h=b5388631\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20110510%2FQQAQLV2AXEYIM55734TZ24ZHY4%2F&h=5bcbe452\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20110510/QQAQLV2AXEYIM55734TZ24ZHY4/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即使海外回來的註冊護士考試及格率也不足四成，<span class=\"red\">內地者更低，更有人連考三次仍不及格</span><br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n立法會議員余若薇表示最近收到投訴，一名在內地有18年工作經驗的資深護士，來港後發現很難搵工，故到護管局查詢報考註冊試的情況，結果發現單是填寫申請表格也極複雜，「<span class=\"red\">連填份表都咁難</span>，佢哋連考試嘅機會都冇」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"blue\">申請表都唔識填 點寫排版<br />\n</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n節錄2014 西方日報 不貼link<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">三次不合格 失重考資格</span><br />\n<br />\n在內地任職護士逾十年的陳女士來港後，以海外護士資歷申請報考香港護士管理局的登記護士執業試。該考試要求若考生三次不能通過執業試，包括筆試及實習試，除非得到特別許可，否則會失去重考資格。<br />\n<br />\n陳聲稱通過筆試後，卻在實習試的考核中遭不公平待遇。她指，實習試要求考生在一小時內完成兩至三項操作，如<span class=\"red\">洗傷口、包紮及攙扶病人</span>等，惟考室規則各有不同，考核前並無通知考生。「A考室畀你一個鐘內做晒所有操作；B考室就要求每個操作做三十分鐘，時間冇得累積」。她指，考室的<span class=\"red\">洗手盆過低</span>，亦令考生難以符合無菌洗手的要求。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"blue\">三十分鐘一個都完成唔到 好意思投訴考試不</span>公<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"blue\">簡單扶抱都唔掂</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">黎到香港只會幫倒忙 多謝曬中國資深護士</span></span>"},{"pid":"68dff48c127997d3fc3157b404d05cd026af85af","tid":2119489,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32f1a792355347a0bca70ca0db7b33ed7464745c","tid":2119489,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:39:54.000Z","msg":"舊聞binC<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n節錄2011年蘋果新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20110510/QQAQLV2AXEYIM55734TZ24ZHY4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20110510%2FQQAQLV2AXEYIM55734TZ24ZHY4%2F&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtB7yOm5tzSGwlZJ%2FCF8Wpw90%3D&h=b5388631\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20110510%2FQQAQLV2AXEYIM55734TZ24ZHY4%2F&h=5bcbe452\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20110510/QQAQLV2AXEYIM55734TZ24ZHY4/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即使海外回來的註冊護士考試及格率也不足